  "title": "Resident Care Officer | Welfare Home",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee the comprehensive care and daily well-being of residents.</li><li>Design, implement, and evaluate a diverse calendar of therapeutic programmes and activities to enhance residents' physical, social, and mental well-being.</li><li>Conduct and document resident reviews and interviews to track progress and personalize care plans.</li><li>Manage the Home's assets, ensuring all equipment is properly maintained and the premises are kept to the highest standards of cleanliness and safety.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min GCE ‘O' level</li><li>Minimum 2 year of experience in the social service sector</li><li>Working Hours: 3 Shift - Rotating Shift </li><li>Willing to work rotating shifts including night shift, weekends and public holidays.</li></ul><p>Check Aber Care Website for more details.</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants may email your updated resume to career@abercare.sg.</p><p><br /></p><p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504</p>",
